'''Breten Vian''' ([[Frenkek]]: ''Bretagne'', [[Bretonek]]: ''Breizh'', [[Gallowek]]: ''Bertaèyn'') yw pow [[keltek]] ystorek war godna-tir an broastir [[Europa|europek]] ynter an [[Chanel]] ha [[Baya Biscay]]. A-dhia an [[Domhwelans Frynkek|Domwhelans Frenkak]] a [[1789]], ma Breten Vian ow qwil radn a'n [[Pow Frynk|Repoblek Frenkek]]. Hanow an pow in [[Kernowek]] a ell inwedh bos '''Lesow''' war-lergh [[Edward Lhuyd]], neb a'y scrifas ev avell ''Lezou''.

Dyberthys yw hei lebmyn yntra dyw ranvro (''régions'') frenkek, '''[[Ranvro Breten Vian]]''' ha '''[[Broyow an Liger|Ranvro Broyow an Liger]]'''. I'n kenja ranvro, ma pejar a'n pemp ''département'' an pow ystorek; an pempes ([[Liger-Atlantek]]) ujy in Broyow an [[Liger]], warbarth gans ''départements'' dhyworth powyow erell (Poitou, Maine, ha Touraine).

==Ystory==
Lies ragadasow a'n Vretonyon a asas [[Breten Veur]] woja an [[Emperoureth Romanek|Romanyon]] dhe omdenna i'n [[5es kansblydhen|410]] [[OK]]. I'n [[9ves kansblydhen|9{{ves}} cansvledhen]], [[Nevenoioù]] (''Nominoë'' yn Frenkek) rug kesunya Breten Vyghan oll in ruwvaneth eudnyk. [[Ancredoryon mor]] a wadnhas an ruwvaneth ma in dalleth an [[10ves kansblydhen|10{{ves}} cansvledhen]]. An ruwvaneth rug kelly Naoned ha'n Liger isel in 909, pan veu Foulque d'Anjou Yurl Naoned. Breten Vian a veu dugeth sempel in-dadn Alan an Lowarn (Alain Barbetorte), neb a rainyas a-dhia 936 bys in 952.

[[Image:Château Nantes 4.JPG|left|thumb|Castell an dhugys, Naoned.]]
Lies Bretonyon a omjunyas dhe drëgh an Normanyon a Vreten Veur in 1066. Anjou ha'n Normanyon, ha woja hedna an Sowson ha Pow Frynk, o in strif dres termyn hir orth maistry war Vreten Vian. In 1203, Conteth Naoned a veu restoryes dhe Vreten Vian; Naoned a venja servya avell bedncita an dhugeth dres termyn hir. Gallowek ha Frenkek a veu an chyf tavosow i'n dhugeth. [[Bresel an Eretons Bretonek]] yntra [[14ves kansblydhen|1341 ha 1364]] a enebas keffrysysy [[Pow Sows]] erbydn keffrysysy [[kurun|curun]] Pow Frynk. Les-serhek era an dhugys i'n termyn na.

:''Erthygel leun a vanylyon: [[Dugeth Vreten Vyghan]].''

Kevambos Unyans a dhywedhas anserhogeth Breten Vian in [[16ves kansblydhen|1532]], bes th'era gen an pow whath omrewl a-jei dhe Bow Frynk bys [[18ves kansblydhen|1789]]. Kerens an Sowson erbydn an [[Domhwelans Frynkek|Domwhelans Frenkak]] o an ''[[Chouanted]]''.

==Gonisogeth==
===Relejyon===
Seyth den sans rug selya [[Kristoneth|Cristoneth]] in Breten Vian: Pawl (Paol/Pol Aurélien) orth Saint-Pol-de-Léon, Tudwal (Tugdual) orth Treger, Briek orth Sen-Briek, Malo orth Sen-Malo, Samzun (Samson) orth Dol, Padern (Paterne) orth Venetens, ha Cowryntin (Kaourintin/Corentin) orth Kemper.

An broassa radn a Vretonyon rug gortos i'n Catholyk Eglos in termyn an Dasfurvyans ha'y woja.

===Tavosow===
[[Image:Breton dialectes.svg|left|thumb|In Breten Vian Awoles (loos), ma tus ow cowsel Gallowek yn hengovek; in Breten Vian Awartha (lywyow erell), mownjei ow cowsel Bretonek.]]
A-dhia an [[Oesow Kres|Osow Cres]], yma dyfrans cler yntra Breten Vian Awartha (i'n Gorlewen: ''Breizh-Izel'' po ''Goueled-Breizh''; ''Basse-Bretagne'') ha Breten Vian Awoles (i'n Est: ''Breizh-Uhel'' po ''Gorre-Breizh;'' ''Haute-Bretagne'' po ''Pays Gallo''). Ma'n broassa nyver a Vretonegoryon in Breten Vian Awartha, le may ma trevow [[Kemper]], [[Brest]], [[An Oryens]], ha [[Venetens]]. In Breten Vian Awoles, in fordh arall, th'era an deythyogyon ow cowsel Gallowek, hag ena yma dyw cita veur ([[Naoned]] ha [[Roazon]]) warbarth gans lies tre arall (rag ensompel, [[Sen Malo]], [[Sen Naser]], [[Pontivy]] ha [[Sen Briek]]). Ma an ‘or’ wonisogethel ow ystydna dhort Sen Briek tu ha tre Venetens.

An 'eth Vretonek re rug gwadnhe a-dhia [[1945]]. Y'n dëdh ma, ma broassa radn an bobel in Breten Vian Awartha hag Awoles ow clappya [[Frenkek]] avell genja tavas anjei. Ma whath 257&nbsp;000 a gowsoryon Bretonek ha 28&nbsp;300 a gowsoryon Gallowek in [[Ranvro Breten Vian]].<ref>Isabelle Le Boëtté (2003). ''[http://www.insee.fr/fr/insee_regions/bretagne/rfc/docs/Oc92art3.pdf Langue bretonne et autres langues : pratique et transmission].'' INSEE.</ref>

==Doronieth==
Costys por hir eus dhe Vreten Vian; ma an mor ow medalhe hin an pow. Yma leun a law ha oll sortow les.

